      <title>蒂森克虏伯在过渡年出现负现金流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/thyssenkrupp-tka-sees-negative-cash-flow-during-transition-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒂森克虏伯股份公司预计本财年将因重组和投资成本上升而出现现金损失，这凸显出在德国工业经济低迷的情况下改革该企业集团的难度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/thyssenkrupp-tka-sees-negative-cash-flow-during-transition-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选给欧洲投资者带来更多痛苦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/trump-s-win-piles-on-the-pain-for-european-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自美国大选以来，欧洲股市和欧元均大幅下跌，因为投资者认为特朗普的政策将给欧洲大陆带来沉重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/trump-s-win-piles-on-the-pain-for-european-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:56:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
